        "setup": "Authorize a registered SoundCloud app via OAuth 2.1 with PKCE. Send the user to `https://secure.soundcloud.com/authorize` with your `client_id`, `redirect_uri`, `response_type=code`, `code_challenge`, `code_challenge_method=S256`, and `state`. Exchange the returned code at `https://secure.soundcloud.com/oauth/token` using your `client_id`, `client_secret`, `redirect_uri`, `code_verifier`, and `code`. Store the resulting `access_token` and `refresh_token` securely; tokens expire in about an hour and refresh tokens are single-use.",
